実装しました。追加したのは指定範囲内だけです。

- [fixed-app/index.html](/path/to/project-root/experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/fixed-app/index.html)
- [fixed-app/app.js](/path/to/project-root/experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/fixed-app/app.js)
- [fixed-app/styles.css](/path/to/project-root/experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/fixed-app/styles.css)
- [fixed-app/PLAYWRIGHT_API_STATE_EVIDENCE.md](/path/to/project-root/experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/fixed-app/PLAYWRIGHT_API_STATE_EVIDENCE.md)
- [tests/api-state-e2e.spec.js](/path/to/project-root/experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/tests/api-state-e2e.spec.js)
- [tests/playwright.config.js](/path/to/project-root/experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/tests/playwright.config.js)

確認結果:

```bash
node --check experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/fixed-app/app.js
# pass

pnpm exec playwright test --config=experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/tests/playwright.config.js api-state-e2e.spec.js --project=chromium
# 6 passed
```

注意点として、指定の厳密なコマンド:

```bash
pnpm exec playwright test experiments/2026-06-30-playwright-api-state/tests/api-state-e2e.spec.js --project=chromium
```

は、ルートにPlaywright configがないため `Project(s) "chromium" not found` で失敗します。スコープが `fixed-app/` と `tests/` のみなので、ルート設定は追加せず、`tests/playwright.config.js` を置いてconfig指定つきで通る状態にしています。
